reviewText: Two Soul Divas in rare form. Starts with Shirley Brown. Sista has a voice reminiscant of The Queen 'Aretha' ... but she's not quite there. Does a pretty good little set ... Then comes Ms Denise LaSalle ,,, a true r$b diva ... works the crowd into a frenzy ... sings all her hits plus some ... nice back up singers and a smokin' band. I was mesmerized Denise has been doing this for a long time and she knows just what to do to move the audience.
